---
title: Sticky Sweet Potato Bibimbap with Spinach, Pickled Cucumber and Sesame Mayo
description: Our Sticky Sweet Potato Bibimbap is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W22_UK_V14558-3_Main_low-68aeecfe.jpg
